<plot>Satyedev, Dharmadhikari, and Buddhiram (Ranjeet, Kader Khan, and Prem Chopra respectively) frame honest, freedom-fighter Jwala Singh (Jeetendra) and have him imprisoned. When Jwala completes his sentence, he seeks out the three so he can avenge himself. And the only person standing in his way is Police Inspector Suraj Kapoor (also Jeetendra), who is none other than Jwala's son.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?477857</url></doc>
